  Auth: requires login (any authenticated user).

FLAGS
  (none)

GLOBAL FLAGS
  --endpoint URL  --request-id ID  --quiet  --verbose  --pretty  --json  --read-only  --asiakas ID

OUTPUT (JSON, stdout)
  no stdout output; exit 0 on success

ERRORS (stderr, exit non-zero)
  exit 1  I/O error              → check file permissions

EXAMPLES
  ib auth logout
"
`;

