exports[`Help snapshots — contract stability > help for ib customer prh matches snapshot 1`] = `
"USAGE
  ib customer prh [<ytunnus>] [flags]

DESCRIPTION
  Look up a company in the Finnish business registry (PRH). Pass <ytunnus> for an exact business-ID lookup, or --search <name>. Read-only; any authenticated user.
  Auth: requires login (any authenticated user).

ARGUMENTS
